## ANTI-PATTERNS (refused)

- ‚ùå Batch op without delegation triplet ‚Äî hook blocks even with [META] tag.
- ‚ùå 2nd+ urgent/high create_task same assignee without `// allow-no-notify` marker ‚Äî hook blocks.
- ‚ùå Multi-task batch with NO consolidated send_message at end ‚Äî assignee orchestrator never picks up.
- ‚ùå `dependsOn: "k17xxx..."` (bare string) ‚Äî must be `["k17xxx..."]` array.
- ‚ùå Title naming the team but not the artifact ("Help Sigma fix something").
- ‚ùå Tagging real batch work as `[META]` to bypass delegation ‚Äî hook detects keywords.

